<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="guarantee-vt">guarantee <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ˌɡærən'tiː/    美 /ˌɡærən'tiː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>保证；确保；担保：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Talent alone isn't enough to guarantee success.
只有天赋是不足以保证成功的。</p><footer>外研新选必① – 2</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>guarantee + that 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Consistent, hard work will guarantee that you will become good at whatever it is. 
坚持不懈和勤奋努力会确保你无论做什么都会做好。</p><footer>2013 广东改</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>guarantee to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We guarantee to behave ourselves tomorrow.
我们保证明天行为规矩。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>提供保修单：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you have the watch cleaned here, we can guarantee it for an additional three months.
如果你在这里清洗手表，我们可以额外保修三个月。</p><footer>2009 天津</footer></div></div>